'''Fievie Afahyɛ''' afenu [[afahyɛ]] a ahenfo ne wɔn manfoɔ a wɔn wɔ Fievie-Dugame a wɔ Tongu Atifi mansin a ɛwɔ Frao Mantam mu wɔ Ghana no di. Wodi saa afahyɛ yi wɔ bosome a ɛtɔ so miensa no mu<ref>https://www.easytrackghana.com/cultural-overview-ghana-festivals.php</ref><ref>https://www.hugedomains.com/domain_profile.cfm?d=ghanaculturepolitics&e=com</ref>

== Afa hyɛ ==
Wɔde nnuane ne nsa gye ahohoɔ wɔ afahyɛ no ase. Amanfoɔ no hyɛ wɔn amammerɛ ntadeɛ ahorɔw de kɔ dwa dataa a ahenfo no abɔ no ase. Asa ne nnwomtoɔ nso kɔ so wɔ afahyɛ no ase<ref>http://www.ghanaembassyiran.com/en/page/majorfestivals</ref>

